emissive - constant color regardless of color conditions
ambient  - fudge factor a constant color to be added
diffuse  - flat matt finish
specular - shiny finish

surface color = emissive + ambient + (for each light: diffuse(light) + specular(light, view))


"Given 2 normalized vectors, the cosine of the angle between them is the dot product"



